      <h1>Container</h1>

      <p class="spirit-subhead">A container is an often-invisible layout element that pushes in from the viewport edges, providing an outer margin and background styling to a row of content. A container often holds the [grid component](/components/grid.html), used for detailed layout within the row. </p>
  {% endfilter %}
{% endblock %}

