    ## Width Options
    Containers come in two widths: <strong>large</strong> and <strong>full-width</strong>. They are identical on smaller devices, only deviating above 1080px viewport width.

    ### Large
    The large container reaches a 1000px maximum width on large viewports.


  {% endfilter %}
