    ### Wave Background
    Use brushes to accent a row by adding waves to a container. The brush sits lower in the z-index than other content, peaking playfully from behind. See various examples below.

    #### Wave 5 Example
    ![wave 5 example](/images/container/wave5.png)

    #### Construction
    1. Set up the container normally, using either <strong>large</strong> or <strong>full-width</strong> size. All container padding options are compatible with brushes.
    * Add a wave svg to the <strong>top</strong> or <strong>bottom</strong> of the container’s content. Follow the code block below.


    #### Wave 5 SVG
  {% endfilter %}

